        <updateDate>2020-02-07T11:55:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stadiums Operating under New Guidance Act or the</b> <b>SONG Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises the authority of the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) to issue temporary flight restrictions for sporting events.</p> <p>The bill requires the FAA to revise the meaning of &quot;sporting&quot; to include all major events held in stadiums, including concerts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
